[{"client_msg_id":"ababab62-496b-470f-a8ae-9608a65913c8","type":"message","user":"U8996GYBF","text":"書いておきました\n\u003chttps://scrapbox.io/yyano/eslint%E3%81%AEwatch%E3%81%AB%E3%81%A4%E3%81%84%E3%81%A6\u003e","ts":"1604728069.232100","attachments":[{"fallback":"Yuki Yano's project: eslintのwatchについて - Yuki Yano's project","id":1,"title":"eslintのwatchについて - Yuki Yano's project","title_link":"https://scrapbox.io/yyano/eslint%E3%81%AEwatch%E3%81%AB%E3%81%A4%E3%81%84%E3%81%A6","text":"eslintの標準にwatchが付いていないので eslint-watch \u003chttps://github.com/rizowski/eslint-watch\u003e を使う eslintの設定そのままだと動いてくれなくてハマった、代わりにonchangeとかを試していた eslintの対象をglobで指定していたんだけど、それだとwatchが発火してくれなかったので --ext オプションとディレクトリの","thumb_url":"https://scrapbox.io/assets/img/content-logo.png","blocks":null,"service_name":"Yuki Yano's project","service_icon":"https://scrapbox.io/assets/img/favicon/apple-touch-icon.png","thumb_width":288,"thumb_height":288,"from_url":"https://scrapbox.io/yyano/eslint%E3%81%AEwatch%E3%81%AB%E3%81%A4%E3%81%84%E3%81%A6","original_url":"https://scrapbox.io/yyano/eslint%E3%81%AEwatch%E3%81%AB%E3%81%A4%E3%81%84%E3%81%A6"}],"team":"T03C4RC8V","reactions":[{"name":"+1","count":1,"users":["UP6PA1UBE"]}],"replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"xGvvz"}]},{"client_msg_id":"f358375a-40d4-4a8e-aa9f-0f2d87feae8a","type":"message","user":"U8996GYBF","text":"```\"lint\": \"eslint --ext .ts src\",\n\"lint:fix\": \"eslint --ext --fix .ts src\",\n\"lint:watch\": \"esw --watch --color --clear --ext .ts src\",```\nこうしました","ts":"1604726854.231800","edited":{"user":"U8996GYBF","ts":"1604727719.000000"},"team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"QkznG"}]},{"client_msg_id":"1377cefa-ebf9-4ab3-95e7-c4d57de594f4","type":"message","user":"U8996GYBF","text":"extオプションで指定してディレクトリ渡す方が適切なのかな、ありがとうございます","ts":"1604726730.231300","edited":{"user":"U8996GYBF","ts":"1604726734.000000"},"team":"T03C4R